data.description: Priced well below market value! Beautiful contemporary style home in the Singletree Estates neighborhood is ready for a new owner! This home is sitting on a large 1/2 acre lot. All bedrooms located on the second level. Custom entryway greets you when you walk in the home. Living room has a beautiful fireplace and off the living room is the formal dining room with custom wainscotting. Great sized kitchen with plenty of cabinet and counter top space with an attached breakfast nook. 1/2 bath also located on the main level. Upstairs you'll find 3 generously sized bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. Less then 10 minutes to shopping, dining and entertainment and only 15 minutes to Fort Campbell and I-24. Fully fenced backyard.
